        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/67e7ee/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-09-09T12:46:09.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi Jason,</p>\n<p>Those look like bottles from Uncle Yu\u2019s in Livermore! I loved the '85 Cuvee L as well, but my favorite of the three was the '88 Cuvee LV, which was just singing when I had a chance to try it. Did you taste the '91 Sauvignon Blanc Reserve as well- that was amazingly young when it was first opened!</p>\n<p>All the Best,</p>\n<p>John</p>",
